{"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error CS0709 | Microsoft Docs\"\n\nms.date: \"2015-07-20\"\nms.prod: .net\n\n\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-csharp\"\n\nms.topic: \"article\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"CS0709\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"CSharp\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"CS0709\"\nms.assetid: 91040f55-a060-4cc3-b830-f6b771af28d7\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"BillWagner\"\nms.author: \"wiwagn\"\n\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\ntranslation.priority.mt: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n---\n# Compiler Error CS0709\n'derived class': cannot derive from static class 'base class'  \n  \n A static class cannot be instantiated or derived from. That is, a static class cannot be a base class of any other class.  \n  \n## Example  \n The following sample generates CS0709.  \n  \n```  \n// CS0709.cs  \n// compile with: /target:library  \npublic static class Base {}  \npublic class Derived : Base {}   // CS0709  \n```","nodes":[{"pos":[12,50],"content":"Compiler Error CS0709 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0709 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,38]}]},{"pos":[565,586],"content":"Compiler Error CS0709","linkify":"Compiler Error CS0709","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error CS0709","pos":[0,21]}]},{"content":"'derived class': cannot derive from static class 'base class'","pos":[587,648]},{"content":"A static class cannot be instantiated or derived from.","pos":[655,709]},{"content":"That is, a static class cannot be a base class of any other class.","pos":[710,776]},{"pos":[785,792],"content":"Example","linkify":"Example","nodes":[{"content":"Example","pos":[0,7]}]},{"content":"The following sample generates CS0709.","pos":[796,834]}]}